Subject: [TSMC] Folder activity details result issue
Description:
AIC version: 11.0.0.95
StealthAUDIT version: 11.0 last version
When selecting to search server activity details, I can get the search results. However, when searching for folder activity details, the search exceeds 30 minutes and ultimately returns no results. Please assist in identifying the root cause and providing a solution.

By the way, I have same issue in my lab.
What_We_Know__c: the customer is on an out-of-support version of NEA and AIC. They are facing issues with scan summary and scan history as the data is not displayed on AIC console.
Next_Steps__c: Issue to be discussed on SWAT
Solution_Comment__c: Dev team has recommended to upgrade as they added an index for effective searching post November 2023 upgrades of NEA and AIC.
